options.text: Quite a place you've got here.
You any good with a sword?

c28b5910-0bf3-469e-8517-320515b95b78.title: <player>
c28b5910-0bf3-469e-8517-320515b95b78.text: Quite a place you've got here.

26df632a-c7e1-4770-8796-e83705df7bf6.title: Harrallak Menarous
26df632a-c7e1-4770-8796-e83705df7bf6.text: Indeed we do. Would you like to know more about it?

options.text: Tell me about the strength training area
Tell me about the attack training area.
Tell me about the defence training area.
Tell me about the combat training area.

81ec349d-b718-4a25-9388-473bf0a75b43.title: <player>
81ec349d-b718-4a25-9388-473bf0a75b43.text: Tell me about the strength training area.

b6d8c6f7-089c-4a7a-a5d2-0dede4b0b5d3.title: Harrallak Menarous
b6d8c6f7-089c-4a7a-a5d2-0dede4b0b5d3.text:
Ahh the mighty warrior Sloane guards the strength
training area. This intriguing little area consists of two
shotput lanes for different weights of shot. It's fairly
simple, the Referee or Sloane can explain more. You

5242159b-53bf-482d-a2e9-8a6cf66e1ef7.title: Harrallak Menarous
5242159b-53bf-482d-a2e9-8a6cf66e1ef7.text: may find yourself panting for breath though.

1f825233-9d2f-4725-b79e-79974f19f224.title: Harrallak Menarous
1f825233-9d2f-4725-b79e-79974f19f224.text:
Well you see my dear, the games there really do
sap your energy quite a bit. You can find it just up
the stairs behind the bank.

a3f1b482-6371-40c8-aae7-47454dd3e528.title: Harrallak Menarous
a3f1b482-6371-40c8-aae7-47454dd3e528.text: Farewell, I do hope you enjoy my guild.

2a3043f5-e07e-4586-8fe1-5631ab2890bc.title: <player>
2a3043f5-e07e-4586-8fe1-5631ab2890bc.text: You any good with a sword?

1e0151e0-70a9-4bc2-9190-d6bde07dafc5.title: Harrallak Menarous
1e0151e0-70a9-4bc2-9190-d6bde07dafc5.text:
Am I any good with....a sword... Have you any clue
who I am?

6d246ad9-2cbe-47ec-950c-2421a93ab315.title: Harrallak Menarous
6d246ad9-2cbe-47ec-950c-2421a93ab315.text: Why I could best any person alive in a rapier duel!

28543561-8fa6-4a78-81d9-29870de8fc81.title: Harrallak Menarous
28543561-8fa6-4a78-81d9-29870de8fc81.text:
My dear, I couldn't possibly duel you, I might
hurt you and then what would happen to my
reputation! Besides, I have this wonderful guild to run.
Why don't you take a look at the various activities we

ad4dd2d1-26e1-45a1-9bf4-c5152f919935.title: Harrallak Menarous
ad4dd2d1-26e1-45a1-9bf4-c5152f919935.text:
have. You might even collect enough tokens to be
allowed in to kill the strange beasts from the east!

49092bfe-5f55-4aae-9d7c-7a41b028eeeb.title: <player>
49092bfe-5f55-4aae-9d7c-7a41b028eeeb.text: Tell me about the attack training area.

a1f0f1cf-8188-4cd0-9c74-2e1beea2e671.title: <player>
a1f0f1cf-8188-4cd0-9c74-2e1beea2e671.text: I'm no dummy, I just want to know what is there!

673c897a-3494-43f3-92bf-48884310cea0.title: Harrallak Menarous
673c897a-3494-43f3-92bf-48884310cea0.text:
Oh no my dear, I did not mean you at all! The
training area has mechanical dummies which pop up out
of holes in the floor. The noble dwarf Gamfred invented
the mechanism and Ajjat can explain more about what

1688bcee-6e6a-43ef-b88b-01cc21ef3c58.title: <player>
1688bcee-6e6a-43ef-b88b-01cc21ef3c58.text: Oh, ok, I'll have to try it out!

9dac22ec-3f0b-4725-b954-e935a0160221.title: Harrallak Menarous
9dac22ec-3f0b-4725-b954-e935a0160221.text:
You can find it just down the corridor and on your
right.

1c813a3b-314c-4a63-a397-860ecbd902bf.title: <player>
1c813a3b-314c-4a63-a397-860ecbd902bf.text: Tell me about the defence training area.

4d013c58-7d27-43d6-9b3f-06f647fea055.title: Harrallak Menarous
4d013c58-7d27-43d6-9b3f-06f647fea055.text:
To polish your defensive skills to the very highest level
we've employed a most inventive dwarf and a catapult.

76da2481-35ff-4034-ab5f-b244a8b754e4.title: <player>
76da2481-35ff-4034-ab5f-b244a8b754e4.text: You're going to throw dwarves at me?

ed7525e5-9fe7-49de-9df4-ce22d85778cc.title: Harrallak Menarous
ed7525e5-9fe7-49de-9df4-ce22d85778cc.text:
Oh my no! I think Gamfred would object to that most
strongly.

aa83f734-6c55-4c75-b633-9e8540811410.title: Harrallak Menarous
aa83f734-6c55-4c75-b633-9e8540811410.text:
He's an inventor you see and has built a marvellous
contraption that can throw all sorts of things at you
including magic missiles...

8ff3be53-d366-47e9-a15c-0900700b45e9.title: Harrallak Menarous
8ff3be53-d366-47e9-a15c-0900700b45e9.text:
No need to be afraid, it's all under very controlled
conditions! You can find it just up the stairs behind the
bank.

7eba5910-ce90-4eee-b792-b4b0863c3413.title: <player>
7eba5910-ce90-4eee-b792-b4b0863c3413.text: Tell me about the combat training area.

2ec00fd3-92b3-4f4e-b6eb-e053ba4059bb.title: Harrallak Menarous
2ec00fd3-92b3-4f4e-b6eb-e053ba4059bb.text:
Ahh yes, our resident magician from foreign lands
created a most amazing gadget which can turn your
own armour against you! It's really quite intriguing.

1a176a77-d570-4fb8-b0d1-7c3870e9e653.title: <player>
1a176a77-d570-4fb8-b0d1-7c3870e9e653.text:
That sounds dangerous. What if I'm wearing it at the
time?

3c69ed52-ca22-4591-84fd-1a8cd0f7f92c.title: Harrallak Menarous
3c69ed52-ca22-4591-84fd-1a8cd0f7f92c.text:
So far that's not happened. You need to speak to
Shanomi about the specifics of the process, but as I
understand it, putting a suit of armour in one of these
devices will make it come to life some how. The better

f15e9c08-6051-4501-b97b-0b40d35927c2.title: Harrallak Menarous
f15e9c08-6051-4501-b97b-0b40d35927c2.text: the armour, the harder it is to 'kill'.

4fe56ec9-aa25-4280-8717-8b113c55042d.title: <player>
4fe56ec9-aa25-4280-8717-8b113c55042d.text:
Fighting my own armour, that sounds... weird. I could
be killed by it...

fec7d8bd-e32e-4706-a82a-d7c4b694cd60.title: Harrallak Menarous
fec7d8bd-e32e-4706-a82a-d7c4b694cd60.text:
Indeed we have had a few fatalities from warriors over
stretching themselves and not knowing their limits. Start
small and work up is my motto! That and go see Lidio
for some food if you need it.

9b6dd43e-4fca-41e5-9208-e39c1cb1c318.title: Harrallak Menarous
9b6dd43e-4fca-41e5-9208-e39c1cb1c318.text:
Ahh, yes, our token system is designed to allow you an
appropriate amount of time with my discovery in the
very top floor of the guild. I won't spoil the surprise as
to what that is. Go up and see for yourself. Now, the

17de70a4-9684-4f84-aab0-32c14efbef66.title: Harrallak Menarous
17de70a4-9684-4f84-aab0-32c14efbef66.text:
amount of tokens you collect from the various activities
around the guild will dictate how long Kamfreena will
allow you in the enclosure on the very top floor. More
tokens equals more time.

0ae614e2-bf4e-411f-a9b8-f7c062dd5726.title: Harrallak Menarous
0ae614e2-bf4e-411f-a9b8-f7c062dd5726.text: If I told you it would spoil the surprise!

82c24452-f384-43bc-b4a1-8905f36e1cec.title: <player>
82c24452-f384-43bc-b4a1-8905f36e1cec.text: Ok ok... so how do I earn and claim these tokens?

cf45b579-3c14-4f6b-bca7-1a7af6903a6d.title: Harrallak Menarous
cf45b579-3c14-4f6b-bca7-1a7af6903a6d.text:
You can earn them simply by using the training
exercises around the guild, the staff will then enter this
into a ledger as you play. You can claim them by
simply asking any of the staff at the training areas, or
